      "content": "i dont know... \"survive the darkness\" still feels like a struggle that doesn't matter. it's just prolonging the inevitable. if you know for a fact the end is coming, isn't it more peaceful to just... not be part of it? to just exit before the pain gets unbearable? it feels more logical than fighting for nothing.",
